folder: Henry Hudson Parkway & 231st Street (West), Bronx, NY
text:
Henry Hudson Parkway (Spuyten Duyvil Parkway), at the N.E. corner
of West 231st Street. The view is northeastward.
May 25, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, from a different angle. The view is southeastward.
May 25, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
